Source: alttab
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Alexander Kulak <sa-dev@rainbow.by>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10), libx11-dev, libxmu-dev, libxft-dev, autoconf, automake, autotools-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.8
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/sagb/alttab.git -b debian/sid
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/sagb/alttab/tree/debian/sid

Package: alttab
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: fonts-dejavu-core
Description: task switcher for minimalistic WMs or standalone X session
 alttab provides convenient visual interface and switching on releasing,
 not pressing Alt key. Being lightweight and depending only on basic 
 X11 libs, it still features customizable look and behaviour.
